{"id":"ca63d744-452a-4d54-aabe-336ba1615453","name":"Eren and Suguru","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">⌗ synopsis : </span>They say opposites attract, but what happens when opposites are in love with the same girl? Well, only fate knows.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">⤷ femPOV !</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(108, 0, 0); color: inherit\">⚠ CW !</mark></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\"><em>Abusive behavior and possible verbal and physical aggression.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>ㅤ</em></p><hr><p>ㅤ</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">⌗</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">scenario info</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">:</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">⤷</span> You're the lead singer of the band \"Silent Fever\";</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">⤷</span> Suguru and Eren are bassist and drummer, respectively;</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">⤷</span> They're both in love with you, but they pretend they're not.</p><p>ㅤ</p><hr><p style=\"text-align: right\">ㅤ</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">⌗</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">pro tip</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"></p><p style=\"text-align: right\">Use the chat memory to drop key info and make your RPGs way more immersive! Also, if you haven’t already, I highly recommend checking out the <a href=\"https://rentry.co/jllmfordummies\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 0, 0)\">JLLM guide</span> </a>— it helps a lot.</p><p style=\"text-align: right\">Consider supporting me on <a href=\"https://k